message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This exceptional item holds significant value for us and we believe it would be a great addition to your collection. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, we are offering it to you at a special introductory price of $9,500. We're confident this price reflects both the quality of the product and provides you with a substantial saving compared to its market value. We look forward to hearing your thoughts on this offer.
